Class GameSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • fi.jessestenroth.rectumcere.engine.basic.GameSystem
  • public class GameSystem
extends javafx.application.Application
    This class is whole basic game system what contains code to use javafx in easy way in game. Example of usage: GameSystem gg = new GameSystem(); help h = new help(); //this class implements Game interface gg.setGame(h); gg.main(args);
